b":{"href":"/us/pl/117/81/s1701/k/3/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–81, § 1701(k)(3)(C)","children":[],"tail":". Instead, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/s1822/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283, § 1822(d)","children":[],"tail":", as added by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/81/s1701/k/3/D"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–81, § 1701(k)(3)(D)","children":[],"tail":", directed the transfer of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2306c"},"text":"section 2306c of this title","children":[],"tail":" in its entirety to this section, thereby omitting what would have been sections 3532 to 3535 of this title. The transfer of section 2306c to this section was executed by transferring the text only of section 2306c, as the section designation and catchline had already been enacted by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/s1822/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283, § 1822(c)","children":[],"tail":", formerly § 1822(m), as renumbered and amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/81/s1701/k/3/A/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–81, § 1701(k)(3)(A)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", (B)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The text of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2306c"},"text":"section 2306c of this title","children":[],"tail":", which was transferred to this section by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/283/s1822/d"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–283, § 1822(d)","children":[],"tail":", as added by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/81/s1701/k/3/D"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–81, § 1701(k)(3)(D)","children":[],"tail":", was based on "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/398/s1/dA"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–398, § 1 [[div. A]","children":[],"tail":", title VIII, § 802(a)(1)], "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-10-30"},"text":"Oct. 30, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/1654"},"text":"114 Stat. 1654","children":[],"tail":", 1654A–203; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107